	      <h2 class="paddingtop"><a href="http://www.brooklynfarmhouse.com/2010/02/17/crock-pot-pulled-pork-or-im-back/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Crock Pot Pulled Pork (or&#8230;I&#8217;m back!)">Crock Pot Pulled Pork (or&#8230;I&#8217;m back!)</a></h2>

	      	      <div class="tellafriend">

<h4 class="floatleft">February 17th, 2010 by megan &middot; <a href="http://www.brooklynfarmhouse.com/2010/02/17/crock-pot-pulled-pork-or-im-back/#comments" title="Comment on Crock Pot Pulled Pork (or&#8230;I&#8217;m back!)">14 Comments</a></h4>

<form class="floatright">
    <input type="image"  value="Print" onclick="window.print()" src="http://www.brooklynfarmhouse.com/wp-content/themes/brooklynfarmhouse_v1.2/images/icon_printer.png" alt="Print this Page" />
</form>

